About
=====

A library to communicate with services of Apple iOS devices using native
protocols.

Requirements
============

Development Packages of:
	libgnutls or openssl
	libplist
	libusbmuxd

Software:
	usbmuxd
	make
	autoheader
	automake
	autoconf
	libtool
	pkg-config
	gcc

Optional:
	cython (Python bindings)
	doxygen (Documentation)

Installation
============

To compile run:
	./autogen.sh --disable-openssl
	make
	sudo make install

iOS 10 Compatibility
====================

As suggested and discussed in the issues of official repository, we need to use GnuTLS instead of OpenSSL along with some other modification contributed from the community (but yet to be merged back to the main repository) to get it working on latest iOS release.

